Definition: an annuity paid in a series of more or less equal payments at the beginning of equally spaced periods
Example: rent payable in advance constitutes an annuity in advance for the landlord
Synonyms: annuity, an, paid, in, a, series, of, more, or, less, equal, payments, at, the, beginning, equally, spaced, periods, rent, payable, advance, constitutes, for, landlord
Category: noun.possession
